    C2["Retained ingress envelope<br>3000 steady eps / 6000 burst eps"]
    C3["Required coupled proof shape<br>steady + burst + recovery with downstream timing and starvation truth"]
  end

  subgraph BLOCKERS["Current Open Blocker Family"]
    B1["Open blocker<br>no dedicated Phase 4 coupled runner yet"]
    B2["Open blocker<br>coupled timing and starvation evidence not yet first-class in the current narrow runner"]
  end

  subgraph POSTURE["Accepted Posture"]
    P1["Keep the promoted runtime and image family pinned"]
    P2["Derive a dedicated coupled runner from the Phase 3 bounded path instead of reusing the older broad PR3-S4 bundle"]
    P3["Add coupled timing and starvation scoring without weakening the retained ingress envelope"]
  end

  subgraph EVIDENCE["Current Evidence Baseline"]
    E1["Phase 3 closure source scope<br>3046.783 eps / 182807 admitted / 4xx = 0 / 5xx = 0"]
    E2["Same source scope proved downstream participation<br>CaseTrigger 2276 / cases 335 / labels accepted 933 / integrity deltas = 0"]
    E3["What remains unproven is the enlarged network under steady + burst + recovery, not the Case + Label plane itself"]
  end

  subgraph VERDICT["Current Verdict"]
    V1["Phase 4 open<br>telemetry and boundary pinned"]
    V2["Next proof target<br>fresh coupled-network validation slice"]
  end

